criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  soccer players;

          -  age of 18-25 years;

          -  a regular attendance at training sessions

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of L1-L5 radiculopathy or lumbo-sacral pathology ;

          -  any treatment with KT on quadriceps or gluteus in the month prior to the study;

          -  history of systemic diseases that may affect the nervous system, musculoskeletal
             injuries or surgeries in the lower limb during the year prior to the study;

          -  use of analgesics or nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs.
